Package: sopravvivenza
Title: Reconstruct Individual Patient Data from Digitized Kaplan-Meier Curves
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Giandomenico", "Bisaccia", , "giandomenico.bisaccia@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for reconstructing individual patient data (IPD) 
    from digitized Kaplan-Meier survival curves using the method described by Guyot et al. 
    This package provides functions for reading digitized curve data, reconstructing IPD, 
    calculating hazard ratios, performing meta-analysis, and creating visualization plots.
